---

<p class="my-8 text-pretty md:text-lg max-w-[740px]">
  En mi viaje por el <span class="text-red-900 dark:text-red-700"
    >mundo del desarrollo web</span
  >, he cultivado <span class="text-red-900 dark:text-red-700"
    >experiencia y habilidades</span
  >. <span class="text-red-900 dark:text-red-700 font-semibold"
    >Mi stack tecnol√≥gico incluye</span
  >:
</p>

<div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 md:grid-rows-2 gap-6 md:place-content-center">
  <!-- Card 1: Frontend -->
  <div
    class="card relative overflow-hidden rounded-2xl
           bg-red-900 dark:bg-red-950
           shadow-2xl border dark:border-neutral-900
           hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow duration-300"
  >
    <div
      class="light-effect absolute w-56 h-56
             bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-900 to-red-900
             dark:from-blue-950 dark:to-red-950
             rounded-full opacity-0 blur-3xl transform
             -translate-x-1/2 -translate-y-1/2
             pointer-events-none transition-opacity duration-300"
    ></div>

    <div class="p-6 relative">
      <h3
        class="text-center mb-8 text-xl font-bold lg:text-4xl
               bg-gradient-to-t from-[#54fbff] to-[#00a4c9]
               dark:from-[#c9fffe] dark:to-[#00cfef]
               bg-clip-text text-transparent"
      >
        Frontend
      </h3>
      <ul class="grid grid-cols-3 gap-4">
        <li class="rounded-2xl group flex flex-col justify-center items-center">
          <HTML class="size-12 mb-2" /><span class="text-sm">HTML</span>
        </li>
        <li class="rounded-2xl group flex flex-col justify-center items-center">
          <CSS class="size-12 mb-2" /><span class="text-sm">CSS</span>
        </li>
        <li class="rounded-2xl group flex flex-col justify-center items-center">
          <JavaScript class="size-12 mb-2" /><span class="text-sm">JavaScript</span>
        </li>
        <li class="rounded-2xl group flex flex-col justify-center items-center">
          <React class="size-12 mb-2" /><span class="text-sm">React</span>
        </li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Card 2: Backend -->
  <div
    class="card relative overflow-hidden rounded-2xl
           bg-red-900 dark:bg-red-950
           shadow-2xl border dark:border-neutral-900
           hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow duration-300"
  >
    <div
      class="light-effect absolute w-56 h-56
             bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-900 to-red-900
